Russell C. McLauchlan, 41 years old, was named president of this biopharmaceutical company.
David M. Goldenberg, 51, who remains chairman, held the position since September 1988, when George Masters resigned.
Mr. Goldenberg controls about 70% of the stock.
Mr. McLauchlan was vice president and general manager of Lederle Laboratories, a unit of American Cyanamid Co. 

